{"title":"Information Management Assessment (IMA) Report","public_updated_at":"2016-10-06T10:36:26Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>As part of the Information Management Assessment (IMA) programme The National Archives conducted a review of information management in the NIO. The programme aims to raise standards and makes recommendations for improvements.</p>\n\n<p>The IMA report published looks at how well the department manages its information and mitigates related risks. The NIO IMA Action Plan presents the departmentâ€™s plans to maintain and improve information management.</p>\n\n<p>The Permanent Secretary Sir Jonathan Stephens welcomed the Report and the examples of current good practice noted, along with the recommendations for further development.</p>\n</div>","change_history":[{"public_timestamp":"2016-10-06T11:36:26.000+01:00","note":"First published."}],"documents":["<section class=\"attachment embedded\" id=\"attachment_1747448\">\n  <div class=\"attachment-thumb\">\n      <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"thumbnail\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/558088/Information_Management_Assessment_report_PDF...pdf\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/558088/thumbnail_Information_Management_Assessment_report_PDF...pdf.png\" /></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"attachment-details\">\n    <h2 class=\"title\"><a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/558088/Information_Management_Assessment_report_PDF...pdf\">Information Management Assessment Report</a></h2>\n    <p class=\"metadata\">\n        <span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">529KB</span>, <span class=\"page-length\">51 pages</span>\n    </p>\n\n\n  </div>\n</section>","<section class=\"attachment embedded\" id=\"attachment_1747449\">\n  <div class=\"attachment-thumb\">\n      <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"thumbnail\" href=\"/government/